{"title":"阿里云盘挂掉后的图床新方案","uid":"1b1f6a596db2be4b9a574d3f216dc869","slug":"图床","date":"2023-02-19T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-02-19T13:20:59.631Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/图床.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-531461443a1378b02ce75e6d78fdfa2e_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b","content":"<h1 id=\"起因\"><a href=\"#起因\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"起因\"></a>起因</h1><p>前几天阿里云盘升级了<code>api</code>，对第三方软件进行了管控，导致我之前使用的<code>OneManager</code>挂载阿里云盘作为图床的方式不能使用了。虽然这一点早在意料之中，但是还是有点突如其来，不免心生悲凉。</p>\n<p>我首先把之前阿里云盘的图片转移到<code>OneDrive</code>，用<code>OneManager</code>重新挂载，保证之前的图片还能正常使用，然后开始思考图床的新方案。</p>\n<h1 id=\"语雀\"><a href=\"#语雀\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"语雀\"></a>语雀</h1><p>语雀兼容原生的<code>markdown</code>语法并支持导出，所以我现在很多笔记都在语雀上写，既方便电脑端，又方便iPad端。然后语雀支持上传5M以内的图片，所以正好在语雀上写好后导出附带图片外链的<code>markdown</code>。</p>\n<p>但是语雀的图片使用了<code>referer</code>防盗链，所以直接在博客中引入是不行的。</p>\n<p>这就到<code>Python</code>和<code>Vercel</code>大显神威的时候了！</p>\n<h1 id=\"思路\"><a href=\"#思路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"思路\"></a>思路</h1><p><code>Vercel</code>部署<code>python</code>项目，<code>python</code>使用<code>requests</code>获取图片内容，再使用<code>flask</code>将图片转发。（缓存+转发）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"># type参数表示要代理的类型: 1为字符串，2为json，3为图片\n@app.route(&#39;&#x2F;proxy&#39;)\ndef proxy():\n    url &#x3D; request.args.get(&#39;url&#39;)\n    header &#x3D; &#123;\n        &#39;User-Agent&#39;: &#39;Mozilla&#x2F;5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit&#x2F;537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome&#x2F;103.0.0.0 Safari&#x2F;537.36&#39;,\n    &#125;\n    res &#x3D; requests.get(url&#x3D;url, headers&#x3D;header)\n    return res.content, 200, &#123;&quot;Content-Type&quot;:res.headers[&quot;Content-Type&quot;], &#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;: &quot;*&quot;&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>然后将语雀的图片链接作为<code>url</code>查询参数即可显示图片了：<code>![](https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/banner/3a89b1120d02254e4fd6bae7d174c60d7a799a4f.png@976w_550h_1c_!web-home-carousel-cover.webp)</code>结果如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/banner/3a89b1120d02254e4fd6bae7d174c60d7a799a4f.png@976w_550h_1c_!web-home-carousel-cover.webp\"></p>\n<p>这个方法具有一定的普适性，对于一些国内无法访问的图片，或者<code>bilibili</code>、语雀等使用了<code>referer</code>防盗链的图片，都有很好的效果。</p>\n<h1 id=\"缺点\"><a href=\"#缺点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"缺点\"></a>缺点</h1><p>这种方式还是有一个明显缺点的，那就是图片不能异步加载，只能串行加载。<code>vercel</code>应该限制了一个云函数不能并发执行。</p>\n<p>但是无关紧要啦~</p>\n","text":"起因前几天阿里云盘升级了api，对第三方软件进行了管控，导致我之前使用的OneManager挂载阿里云盘作为图床的方式不能使用了。虽然这一点早在意料之中，但是还是有点突如其来，不免心生悲凉。 我首先把之前阿里云盘的图片转移到OneDrive，用OneManager重新挂载，保证之...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"分享","slug":"分享","count":11,"path":"api/categories/分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vercel","slug":"Vercel","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Vercel.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%B5%B7%E5%9B%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">起因</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AF%AD%E9%9B%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">语雀</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">思路</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BC%BA%E7%82%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">缺点</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fi